We examined specimens of
L. simile
from the two known localities: the type-locality Grieta Punta de Guana cave (Nalbant, 1981) and La Pluma Cave (
Diaz-Perez et al. 1987a
). This species was also reported from El Tunel cave in Quivican, southern Havana, living in sympatry with
L. dentata
(
Diaz-Perez et al. 1987a
). However, this later report need verification.
